data.description: Welcome to this four-bedroom home that offers a perfect blend of modern and timeless charm. Inviting porch, updated kitchen featuring newer countertops, a stylish backsplash, updated appliances, living room and dining room have been freshly painted and adorned with new carpeting. Completing the main floor is a convenient bedroom and bathroom. Upper level includes three additional bedrooms, providing ample space. Numerous windows have been replaced, ensuring natural light and energy efficiency. A tuck under garage is great for parking and storage. Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming home yours!
